⍝ Reshape.tc
⍝ ══════════

      ⎕IO←1

      ⍝ Precond: A simple scalar/vector nonneg integers
      ⍝ inv: ⍴Z ←→ ,A
      ⍝ inv: ⍴⍴Z ←→ ⍴,A
      A ← 2 3 4                               ⍝ target shape
      B ← ⎕RVAL 1 (,24) (,0 1 0 0 0)
      Z ← A⍴B
      (⍴Z) ≡ ,A
1
      (⍴⍴Z) ≡ ⍴,A
1
      ⍝ Scalar A reshapes to vector
      A ← 3+4∣|⎕RVAL 0                       ⍝ A in 3..6
      B ← ⎕RVAL 0
      Z ← A⍴B
      (⍴Z) ≡ ,A
1
